18 from becoming an emergency medical condition; and (2) the Department grants
19 prior approval for such care based on the medical necessity of the care.
20 Section 2 of this bill makes a conforming change to require the Director of the
21 Department to administer the provisions of section 1 in the same manner as other
22 provisions relating to Medicaid.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF NEVADA, REPRESENTED IN
